ZH: 我们计划参观附近的修道院。
EN: We plan to visit the nearby monastery.

ZH: 这座修道院有着悠久的历史。
EN: This monastery has a long history.

ZH: 很多人来这个修道院寻求宁静与冥想。
EN: Many people come to this monastery seeking peace and meditation.

ZH: 这座修道院位于山脚下，风景优美。
EN: This monastery is located at the foot of the mountain with beautiful scenery.

ZH: 修道院的建筑风格独特，具有当地特色。
EN: The architecture of the monastery is unique and reflects the local style.

ZH: 这个修道院是一个重要的宗教遗址。
EN: This monastery is an important religious site.

ZH: 修道院的内部装饰非常精美，充满神秘感。
EN: The interior decoration of the monastery is exquisitely done and filled with a sense of mystery.

ZH: 我们在修道院里欣赏到了美丽的宗教艺术。
EN: We were able to appreciate beautiful religious art inside the monastery.

ZH: 修道院的院子里有一个宁静的花园。
EN: There is a peaceful garden in the courtyard of the monastery.

ZH: 修道院的门口有一块巨大的石碑。
EN: There is a huge stone tablet at the entrance of the monastery.

ZH: 这个修道院每天都会举行宗教仪式。
EN: This monastery holds religious ceremonies every day.

ZH: 这座修道院被周围的群山环绕着。
EN: This monastery is surrounded by mountains.

ZH: 修道院是一个适合修行的地方。
EN: The monastery is a suitable place for spiritual practice.

ZH: 天气晴朗的日子，修道院的屋顶反射着阳光。
EN: On sunny days, the roof of the monastery reflects sunlight.

ZH: 修道院的钟声可以传遍整个山谷。
EN: The sound of bells from the monastery can be heard throughout the valley.

ZH: 这个修道院也提供住宿和食品给朝圣者。
EN: This monastery also provides accommodation and meals for pilgrims.

ZH: 修道院的修道士们每天早晚都会进行祈祷和冥想。
EN: The monks in the monastery pray and meditate every morning and evening.

ZH: 这座修道院拥有一个宏伟的礼拜堂。
EN: This monastery has a magnificent chapel.

ZH: 修道院的大门上刻着古老的经文。
EN: Ancient scriptures are engraved on the door of the monastery.

ZH: 我们在修道院遇到了一位友好的修道士。
EN: We met a friendly monk at the monastery.
